{"nodes": [{"id": "docs_superpowers_plans_2026_07_08_spotmap_stage6_architecture_onpush_signals_zonejs", "label": "OnPush + Signals, Keep Zone.js", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "docs/superpowers/plans/2026-07-08-spotmap-stage6-architecture.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Recorded user decision: adopt ChangeDetectionStrategy.OnPush across all 10 components with signal-driven state but keep Zone.js (NOT zoneless) \u2014 a low-risk migration since state is already signal-driven; any imperatively-mutated binding is converted to a signal to stay live under OnPush."}, {"id": "docs_superpowers_plans_2026_07_08_spotmap_stage6_architecture_for_control_flow", "label": "@for Control Flow Migration", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/superpowers/plans/2026-07-08-spotmap-stage6-architecture.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Migrate *ngFor to the new @for control flow with correct track expressions (loading-bar matrix loops MUST track $index to avoid NG0955 duplicate-key; map city select tracks entry.key / city.city), rendered output identical."}, {"id": "docs_superpowers_plans_2026_07_08_spotmap_stage6_architecture_signal_input_output", "label": "Signal input()/output() API", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/superpowers/plans/2026-07-08-spotmap-stage6-architecture.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Convert ascii-animation-text @Input() messages / @Output() animationFinished to signal input<string[]>() and output<void>() (binds identically, so no template change), aligning with the standalone+signals constraint."}, {"id": "docs_superpowers_plans_2026_07_08_spotmap_stage6_architecture_glyph_measurement", "label": "Reliable ASCII Glyph Measurement", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/superpowers/plans/2026-07-08-spotmap-stage6-architecture.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Measure the real rendered advance of --font-mono (canvas measureText or a hidden measuring element), recompute on resize, and guard against zero/NaN measurement so the ASCII grid stays aligned in IBM Plex Mono without changing animation cadence; also fixes the global-querySelector scoping bug."}, {"id": "docs_superpowers_plans_2026_07_08_spotmap_stage6_architecture_router_driven_nav", "label": "Router-Driven Navigation", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/superpowers/plans/2026-07-08-spotmap-stage6-architecture.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Fix the unawaited this.router.navigate([''] ) in AppComponent.ngOnInit (masked today by the wildcard **\u2192home route); make the intro\u2192content flow explicit/awaited and router-driven with the nav-bar's RouterLink, keeping the default landing behavior identical."}], "edges": [{"source": "docs_superpowers_plans_2026_07_08_spotmap_stage6_architecture_onpush_signals_zonejs", "target": "docs_superpowers_plans_2026_07_07_spotmap_audit_refactor_stage6_architecture", "relation": "implements", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "docs/superpowers/plans/2026-07-08-spotmap-stage6-architecture.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "docs_superpowers_plans_2026_07_08_spotmap_stage6_architecture_for_control_flow", "target": "docs_superpowers_plans_2026_07_07_spotmap_audit_refactor_stage6_architecture", "relation": "implements", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "docs/superpowers/plans/2026-07-08-spotmap-stage6-architecture.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "docs_superpowers_plans_2026_07_08_spotmap_stage6_architecture_signal_input_output", "target": "